result.RESTART: Reload config file and restart host software
result.FIRMWARE_RESTART: Restart firmware, host, and reload config
result.HELP: Report the list of available extended G-Code commands
result.SET_GCODE_OFFSET: Set a virtual offset to g-code positions
result.RESTORE_GCODE_STATE: Restore a previously saved G-Code state
result.GET_POSITION: Return information on the current location of the toolhead
result.SET_PRINT_STATS_INFO: Overwrite, to get pause_next_layer and pause_at_layer feature
result.SDCARD_RESET_FILE: Clears a loaded SD File. Stops the print if necessary
result.SDCARD_PRINT_FILE: Loads a SD file and starts the print.  May include files in subdirectories.
result.CLEAR_PAUSE: Clears the current paused state without resuming the print
result.SET_DISPLAY_TEXT: Set or clear the display message
result.RESPOND: Echo the message prepended with a prefix
result.SET_GCODE_VARIABLE: Set the value of a G-Code macro variable
result.SET_PAUSE_NEXT_LAYER: Enable a pause if the next layer is reached
result.SET_PAUSE_AT_LAYER: Enable/disable a pause if a given layer number is reached
result._TOOLHEAD_PARK_PAUSE_CANCEL: Helper: park toolhead used in PAUSE and CANCEL_PRINT
result._CLIENT_EXTRUDE: Extrudes, if the extruder is hot enough
result._CLIENT_RETRACT: Retracts, if the extruder is hot enough
result._CLIENT_LINEAR_MOVE: Linear move with save and restore of the gcode state
result.SET_PIN: Set the value of an output pin
result.STEPPER_BUZZ: Oscillate a given stepper to help id it
result.QUERY_ENDSTOPS: Report on the status of each endstop
result.SET_IDLE_TIMEOUT: Set the idle timeout in seconds
result.TUNING_TOWER: Tool to adjust a parameter at each Z height
